{
  "title": "Beat Bank",
  "children": [
    {
      "title": "Overview",
      "lines": [
        "~100 fixed drum",
        "patterns across many",
        "genres. No randomness.",
        "",
        "Load it as the MIDI FX",
        "in front of a drum kit",
        "and press Play. The",
        "pattern plays straight",
        "and follows Move's",
        "tempo - Beat Bank has",
        "no tempo or swing of",
        "its own."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Selecting Patterns",
      "lines": [
        "Open the slot's MIDI",
        "FX (Beat Bank). Menu:",
        " - Pattern: scroll to",
        "   change it (live).",
        " - Pattern View: full",
        "   grid view + Print",
        "   (jog scrolls, Pad1",
        "   Print, Pad2 Play/",
        "   Stop). Jog-click or",
        "   Back exits it.",
        " - Drum Notes (submenu)",
        " - Swap Module / None"
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Drum Notes",
      "lines": [
        "In the Drum Notes",
        "submenu, 12 voices each",
        "send a GM drum note",
        "(kick 36, snare 38,",
        "hats 42/46 ...).",
        "",
        "Move kits vary, so map",
        "by ear: scroll a voice",
        "and you HEAR that note",
        "fire on the kit. Stop",
        "when you hear the kick,",
        "then snare, etc."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Print to Move",
      "lines": [
        "Capture a pattern as a",
        "real Move clip:",
        "",
        "1 Slot MIDI FX mode ->",
        "  Schw+Move; Receive",
        "  Ch = the drum track.",
        "2 Mute the slot. Open",
        "  Pattern View; Pad2",
        "  to Stop the loop.",
        "3 On Move: arm Record",
        "  + start transport.",
        "4 Pad1 (Print) fires",
        "  ONE clean bar; Move",
        "  records it.",
        "5 Switch Move pattern,",
        "  repeat."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Sync",
      "lines": [
        "Beat Bank follows",
        "Move's transport over",
        "MIDI clock. It needs",
        "Settings -> MIDI ->",
        "MIDI Clock Out -> On,",
        "and the transport",
        "running, or it stays",
        "silent."
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Add Your Own",
      "lines": [
        "Patterns are plain",
        ".beat text files. Drop",
        "your own in:",
        " UserData/schwung/",
        "  beatbank/patterns/",
        "",
        "See _HOWTO.txt there",
        "for the format. Your",
        "patterns appear after",
        "the built-ins."
      ]
    }
  ]
}
